metadata.name: Lust | Hope
metadata.description:
Our bodies are our only true home.
We hope that one day weâ€™ll embrace every part of it.
What we wear and how we wear it brings us closer to that hope.
The hope that takes away your lust to rape us and shame us.
The lust that moves you to label and divide us.
We lust for a world free from your eyes.
The eyes that hope to get a peek up our skirt
